i'm changing.
people i found i really wanted to be friends with last year.. i no longer have the want to be friends with.
i still love all my theatre people.
but in some instances i fing everyone i bit to gossipy.
no i know that i still do and still want to know things.
but these last couple of days i just havent cared.
i dont mind listening to peoples problems.
and there is that one person that i might tell SOME things to that arent all that important...
but i sont care about who hates who.. thats their fucking problem and they need to deal with it themselves.
and i hate it when i try to confront people about how i KNOW they feel.. yet they deney it and
i hate feeling like this person is trying to compete with me over everything but i just dont fucking care and they don't get it
i hate hearing how i told someone something and they went and told all these people and now these people know about some part of me i didnt want them to know about.
i just dont like the thought of people talking about people.. and lately.. i just havent had a need to do it or hear about it.
and i want people to be honest for once.
say how they really feel.
i'm getting sick of fucking coded messages.
why cant people just say it.
just say how they feel
instead of hiding it.


..i dunno maybe i hate people right now.
there really isnt anyone who is REALLY close to me.
and for some reason i dont mind.
i've always had a best friend.
but i like that i dont
i just have friends i tell somethings and others i tell other things.

i just most of my friends.
but alot right now are just fun to hang with.
even though the things they are doing are kinda annoying... and i find them less and less attractive people as it goes along.

ahh fucking losers.

^thats my new one guys. have fun

he doesnt understand that its about spending time with my parents.
its not about a scheudule.
its about each parent getting equal time with me.

instead he makes a big deal out of something that isnt.

just the thought of him makes me frustrated.

hah.. thats funny.. its pushing me away dumbass.



god i fucking hate him

and i'm sad.. and confused.

so confused.

i really dont wanna go to school.

today was... normal?

nothing interesting happend.. no life changing moments

there is a feeling building up and if i dont do something about it soon.. it will explode.

life is somewhat simple. things seem to be going... better?

but something isnt right. and there is a specific tension i need to focus on and want to focus on.. humph.



joy...

today went so much smoother then i expected and i thank god for everyone.
:)

i went to swimteam.. i had no idea how long it had been since i had been swimming.. i am so out of shape.. ugh.. i hate it wheni have to rebuild my indurance which was never that wonderful in the first place and i came to school and i was so tired and i NNEEEEDDD to finish my journals but the tiredness is taking over. ugh!and ineed to sleep early b/c i need to wake up early. 

if i had a car i would skip wednesday.
i would skip so may days.
well.. actually only one every now and again.

and i cant wait till wednesday.. i get to be with my mommie.. i miss her so much. its such a nice change from my dad. i have more patience and respect from her which inturn helps me have more patience and respect with her. and shes been outta town and i havent been able to see her forever.
i love her so much.

otherwise it was an ok day.
there were things that i would have liked to change
a person i wanted to talk to more. but to nervous. haha

ok first off.. i am not looking for sympathy and for people to reply to this b/c i know it is the truth and i know that you have all heard it from someone else already and you all probably feel the same about me right now.


but i am a bitch
i was thinking only of myself.
and i go through the phases where i think only of myself
b/c i am changing
and i find different people and things to do
and i dont mean to hurt anyone
and it brings me to tears for what i did b/c i hate hurting people
and i genuinely dont mean to
but i do have a bad tendency and i recognize it
but i'm going through some of my  changes and i cant  change everything and i know i still act like a 5th grader in some aspects about this and i just wish i wasnt so self centered at times

and i dont mean to
i just feel like i'm doing everything wrong and nothing right

b/c i dont think.. i just do
and i think only about my happiness and not tohers
and i just wish i was as sweet as some of the people i know
and thought 

i would do anything to take it back. and now is when i am desperate for that time machine

i just dont know what has come over these past couple of weeks
i really need someone to help me and i am looking everywhere so i go off to places and just try to find someone to help me and raise my self esteem b/c it is really low right now and i have no idea why. and everything is going wrong and i am trying to stay my usual self and its so hard. i am loosing track of all the things i once beleived in and starting to forget my own morals. i feel like i'm headed in a downward spiral.i just want to grow up and be able to be mature about situations.i'm just afraid my time is running out.. i'm afraid these next years will go by in such a hurry that i wont realize what the fuck is going on andf th next thing youll know ill end up a loser on the streets. and i dont want that to happen. i'm afraid of my future.. and i know this is so weird but i want to die before i get out in the real world b/c i believe i wont be able to take care of myself and i will end up one of those stay at homes moms that takes care fo the children but i want to do something and be someone i've lost my passion and i dont know where to find it and i'm so scared. i'm so scared i'm losing who i once was. i want to be innocent again.i want to not know anything i wangt to start over.and do and try my best.and i hate myself so much right now i feel like a bitch.. i have never felt so horrible. i just want to shrivle up and die. 


none rant part.
[and the sad thing is all the people i know are probably really dissappointed and angry with me andthis is were i apoligize to them b/c i didnt mean to i didnt realize how much it effected people b/c it really doesnt effect me all that much and i was assuming everyone was me the reason i am not going to you one at time is b/c i dont know everyone who knows. all i can ask of you is to tell me when this is happening and warn me about it b/c i really do wanna change it. and i need to start realizing that i do affect other people and i do hurt other people and i need to stop being cruel. i hope all of the people i have offended without realizing it can realize  am being sincere and didint mean to offend them and that they have ti in their hearts to forgive and understand]

i have just discovered my dads goal in life this week:

to see how much he can make me cry.

he digs and won't shut up. and maybe i'm just being over emotional but god it hurts.. everything. i care. but people dont understand that.

otherwise..
i had an awesome night

today was emotional.
there was so much to remeber and i am already forgetting.

life is just kinda a whirl right now.
i'm not really sure what i'm doing but i know exactly what i'm feeling.
i dunno just the premise.

i need support.. that i can trust..
and i know i have so much around me and i am surrounded by it everyday
and i talked to someone today about it a little.
and i like that i like confiding in them.
but i want someone else.. someone that i dont have right now
and want dearly.

blah.. well back to some other form of entertainment

..i feel out of place and discarded


i don't belong anywhere anymore..
and i don't belong with anyone anymore.






and holy shit am i frightened

why is nothing going right?
my days have been nothing but horrible
though at times i am my usual self b/c pva just does that to people..
something always finds a way to pull me back to reality for a coupla of hours

what am i doing wrong?
what do i need to do right?

..i don't remember the last time i actually remember having a good day.
and i hate the feeling of having tears in the back of my head the entire day so if i am not talking i am just thinking nothign goes right.

and i have to go to fucking college station this weekend.
i just wanna run away.
theres just ganna be another fight anyways..
i hate family trips so much.
why cant i just stay here.
i know who to hang with to have a good time. who i need at the moment.

i just hate being me right now and i need to be around people who can make me forget.
thank god i have friends that can do that.



where is my mind?

i am so confused.
mixed feelings.
i really think it's just this house.


i have been looking forward to school and wish i could just stay there lately.

i don't see whynot

during 3 months i spent more time at school then home including weekends.

i wouldnt mind doing it again.

and it isnt even like anything bad has happened here.
so far...


i just cna't stand being here around these people that are my suposed family. i have no privacy when i get home from school.. when i need it most. when i need to sit and think about the day.. they don't give it to me. 




god stupid people.

i hate being here.
i hate everyone around me when i'm here.
i just wish i was somewhere else
some other persons house.
someone that can make me happy.

this place depresses me.

o just wish everything was like it was before.



perfect...

school still goes great.
even though i stil wish summer was hear.
it will get all crappy like and stressie about a month or so in.

and then everyone will moan and groan.. and will start having breakdowns etc. etc.

oh the joy of pva.

still somewhat confused...

but i think that it might just be temporary.

doubts are starting
but i hope that its a wall.


in some ways school sucks..
i dont have enough free time.

it was fun. 
i enjoyed seeing everyone.
i enjoyed meeting new people.
i enjoyed having my friends around me again.
i enjoyed having work.
i enjoyed having something to do.
i enjoyed being in theatre.

but most of all


i enjoyed me and claras wonderful song!


ok well i'm off the comp for awhile.. going to dads.. and i just need to stop being so addicted.

school starts tomorrow.

i'm excited to see everyone! i'm excited to have something to do! i'm excited to just be back!

even though i'm dreading every last bit.


yesterday i got a haircut.. i mucho like :D
then did some back to school shopping...
saw scott XD XD XD XD

and now i have to wash my very VERY dirty dog.

life is good right now.
thanks god.

very eventful week.

lots of shtuff.

summer review
i had fun. it had it's boring times but right round the end of it it started to become interesting.. i got busy seeing all my theatre peeps and leah.. i hooked up with scott. new jersey and mississippi were great even though they had their moments like all things. and i got excited for school to start.. academics and all.. i just want the feeling of walking into that building again.. for some reason it gives off such a great feeling but you don't realize it anymore by the time you need to remember it to keep you going. but atleast i want to go back to school.. not like johnston where i dreaded every bit of it. 


oh yes and thanks to clara for my new and improved journal

then clara and anna came over and we watched pulp fiction. AGAIN.. but i love that movie.. 

got ready and went to mr singletons thing which has to be one of the best nights i've had in awhile.. it was so eventful and everything. i got to hang out with my theatre people who i didn't realize i had missed so much.. i'm glad i got the time away from them b/c it made me realize how much i missed them.. and i also made sure me and lindsey were cool.. and we are.. yay!

clara is over YAYAYAYAYAYAYAY.. i missed that crizazy mofo of a twinkie..:D

everything is just going so smoothely i'm actually looking forward to my future and it's so great!!!!!!

..i can't wait till scott gets back
